==English==
===Etymology===
Old English [[geard|ġeard]].

==== Noun ====
'''yard''' (''plural'' '''[[yards]]''')

# The land surrounding a house and belong to the owner of the house.
# (''Jamaican'') One's house or home.
# (''Jamaican'') Jamaica (''used by Jamaicans when abroad'')

==== Translations ====
*French: (1): [[cour]] ''f''
*Italian: (1): [[cortile]] ''m''
*Swedish: [[gård]] (1), [[trädgård]] (1), [[tomt]] (1)

